name: Mosesdb
tagline: A simple database created for fun and profit
body: # Welcome to mosesDB! ## The simple, small-scale database for non-critical data [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/DannyMoses/mosesDB.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/DannyMoses/mosesDB) To get started: 1. Download the repository. 1. Unpack the repository. 1. Run `./compile` 1. Create a schema(template) like the one provided 1. Enjoy! ### mosesDB has NO DEPENDENCIES and very little reliance on the C standard library! ## Feel free to contribute, there is still much that needs to be done!
